diff:1097760793:1097760734:=1,14c1%0a%3c ! Software Raid's%0a%3c  1. Install Lilo 22.6%0a%3c %0a%3c  2. mdadm -a /dev/md0 /dev/sda1 -> (4 disks=[UUUU])%0a%3c %0a%3c  3. mount /dev/md1 /mnt/newroot (do not yet hot-add the 4th disk!)%0a%3c %0a%3c  4. mount /dev/md0 /mnt/newroot/boot%0a%3c %0a%3c  5. Edit lilo.conf so boot = /dev/md0%0a%3c %0a%3c  6. Lilo -x mbr (Thanks John!!)%0a%3c %0a%3c  7. The End: Do not forget to 'fd' /dev/sda1 and /dev/sda3%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a---%0a> ! Software Raid's%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
host:1097760793=80.219.133.159
